    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! I've taken great care of it, so it's clean and ready to hit the road immediately. If you're looking for a reliable car that looks great and runs even better, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
