    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates, and the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal camshaft phasing. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings and factory-spec dampening. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain integrity is excellent, maintaining consistent compression across all six cylinders. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize analog feedback and longitudinal G-forces.",
